1
00:00:14,469 --> 00:00:17,917
Laut tak nampak indah hari ini.

2
00:00:18,597 --> 00:00:21,619
Tapi laut indah atau tak, tak penting pun.

3
00:00:22,515 --> 00:00:24,062
Sebab bagi aku,

4
00:00:24,580 --> 00:00:26,157
ia sama saja setiap hari.

5
00:00:32,336 --> 00:00:34,112
Tapi langit—

6
00:00:34,880 --> 00:00:36,671
tak pernah sama walau sehari pun.

7
00:00:37,825 --> 00:00:39,866
Tapi tetap memukau.

8
00:00:41,522 --> 00:00:43,808
Entah kau pun tengok langit yang sama.

9
00:00:54,952 --> 00:00:57,854
Masa kecil, bila aku sedih,

10
00:00:58,088 --> 00:01:00,308
aku selalu datang sini untuk menyorok.

11
00:01:01,087 --> 00:01:04,814
Tempat ni markas rahsia kita.

12
00:01:16,973 --> 00:01:18,703
Phoon... Phoon.

13
00:01:18,958 --> 00:01:19,961
Phoon.

14
00:01:20,991 --> 00:01:22,657
Fah dah sampai.

15
00:01:24,936 --> 00:01:27,724
Cuma dia yang aku harap jumpa aku.

16
00:01:34,247 --> 00:01:35,241
Phoon.

17
00:01:36,645 --> 00:01:38,047
Fah ada ni.

18
00:01:39,303 --> 00:01:40,863
P'Fah.

19
00:01:40,976 --> 00:01:42,837
Dan dia selalu berjaya cari aku.

20
00:01:45,585 --> 00:01:47,297
- Tak apa, Phoon.
- P'Fah.

21
00:01:47,518 --> 00:01:49,602
Tak apa. Aku ada sini.

22
00:01:50,262 --> 00:01:53,100
- P'Fah.
- Tak payah takut, Phoon.

23
00:01:54,554 --> 00:01:56,262
P'Fah.

24
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:33,282
Kau pergi mana? Ada sakit kat mana-mana?

25
00:02:33,312 --> 00:02:34,562
Mak dan ayah belum balik lagi.

26
00:02:34,677 --> 00:02:35,854
Jangan takut.

27
00:02:36,001 --> 00:02:37,462
Aku takkan beritahu mak dan ayah.

28
00:02:37,586 --> 00:02:39,773
yang kau keluar senyap-senyap nak main.

29
00:02:40,290 --> 00:02:42,330
- Betul?
- Mestilah.

30
00:02:43,527 --> 00:02:45,650
Terima kasih, Fah, hantar Phoon balik.

31
00:02:46,171 --> 00:02:47,274
Kalau macam tu, saya balik dulu.

32
00:02:47,405 --> 00:02:50,020
Nanti mak ayah tahu kami keluar lewat.

33
00:02:50,291 --> 00:02:52,871
- Nanti aku kena marah lagi.
- Okey. Bye-bye.

34
00:02:54,979 --> 00:02:55,949
Jom. Masuk.

35
00:03:24,477 --> 00:03:26,856
Aku ingat kita dapat sekolah menengah sama lagi.

36
00:03:27,506 --> 00:03:28,613
Ruginya.

37
00:03:28,853 --> 00:03:31,216
Habis siapa nak tutor aku dan Phoon?

38
00:03:31,785 --> 00:03:33,684
Fun dan Phoon dah pandai belajar.

39
00:03:34,290 --> 00:03:35,854
Aku akan belajar rajin.

40
00:03:36,124 --> 00:03:37,515
Aku akan masuk sekolah perubatan.

41
00:03:37,777 --> 00:03:39,278
Dan jadi doktor macam kau, Fah.

42
00:03:39,610 --> 00:03:40,835
Aku pun akan usaha.

43
00:03:41,188 --> 00:03:42,368
Jom jadi doktor sama-sama.

44
00:03:42,897 --> 00:03:45,407
Jangan lupa kami bila dah ada jiran baru, ya?

45
00:03:45,579 --> 00:03:47,435
Ala... aku takkan lupa korang.

46
00:03:50,500 --> 00:03:51,441
Phoon.

47
00:03:53,731 --> 00:03:55,567
Mungkin lama kita tak jumpa.

48
00:03:55,854 --> 00:03:57,016
Jaga diri elok-elok.

49
00:03:59,019 --> 00:03:59,524
Ya.

50
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:09,201
Baik, budak-budak. Mari ambil gambar.

51
00:04:11,850 --> 00:04:14,100
Mari, rapat sikit.

52
00:04:16,054 --> 00:04:19,225
Okey. Satu, dua, tiga.

53
00:04:19,838 --> 00:04:21,017
Tukar tempat.

54
00:04:21,180 --> 00:04:24,210
Tukar kiri kanan, cepat.

55
00:04:26,014 --> 00:04:28,805
Satu, dua, tiga.

56
00:04:29,060 --> 00:04:31,520
Satu, dua, tiga.

57
00:05:00,466 --> 00:05:03,465
Cik Theerapa Chaowakornkul
Lahir: 13 September 1996
Meninggal: 10 Oktober 2013

58
00:05:03,475 --> 00:05:04,675
Phoon datang nak ucap selamat tinggal.

59
00:05:08,573 --> 00:05:10,038
Selamat tinggal, Fun.

60
00:05:29,303 --> 00:05:30,225
Ya, Pak Cik Kong.

61
00:05:30,616 --> 00:05:32,148
Kenapa pergi awal sangat?

62
00:05:32,546 --> 00:05:34,074
Bukan penerbangan kau petang ni?

63
00:05:35,257 --> 00:05:36,878
Saya singgah jumpa Fun dulu.

64
00:05:37,186 --> 00:05:38,152
Kenapa tak beritahu Pak Cik?

65
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,374
Pak Cik boleh hantar kau ke lapangan terbang.

66
00:05:39,514 --> 00:05:41,589
Pak Cik tak perlu tolong ayah saya kerja ke?

67
00:05:42,183 --> 00:05:43,503
Saya tak nak susahkan Pak Cik.

68
00:05:43,776 --> 00:05:45,413
Susah? Taklah.

69
00:05:46,004 --> 00:05:48,576
Kau pasti boleh pergi lapangan terbang sendiri?

70
00:05:50,322 --> 00:05:51,186
Ya, boleh.

71
00:05:51,896 --> 00:05:55,299
Nanti Pak Cik poskan barang kau yang lain.

72
00:05:55,570 --> 00:05:56,980
Kalau perlukan apa-apa, bagitahu Pak Cik.

73
00:05:57,194 --> 00:06:01,531
Kau ke Chiang Mai seorang diri. Pak Cik risau.

74
00:06:04,837 --> 00:06:05,912
Terima kasih.

75
00:06:06,472 --> 00:06:08,143
Hati-hati jalan.

76
00:06:10,142 --> 00:06:10,632
Ya.

77
00:06:19,746 --> 00:06:20,557
Fun.

78
00:06:21,832 --> 00:06:23,666
Phoon nak pergi jumpa P'Fah sekarang.

79
00:09:49,841 --> 00:09:51,841
Kepada: Torfun

80
00:09:52,863 --> 00:09:54,662
Aku dah sampai di Chiang Mai.

81
00:09:55,016 --> 00:09:56,453
Aku baru sampai asrama.

82
00:09:56,837 --> 00:09:58,745
Semester nak mula tak lama lagi.

83
00:09:59,121 --> 00:10:01,336
Aku betul-betul rasa bersalah pada kau, Fun.

84
00:10:01,671 --> 00:10:05,542
Sebab gagal peperiksaan masuk sekolah perubatan.

85
00:10:05,764 --> 00:10:07,721
Aku nak jadi doktor untuk kau.

86
00:10:08,254 --> 00:10:10,065
Tapi tahun depan, aku pasti berjaya.

87
00:10:20,343 --> 00:10:21,951
Cuaca hari ni elok.

88
00:10:22,361 --> 00:10:26,914
Aku nak keluar ambil gambar.
Doakan aku tak sesat lagi.

89
00:10:44,921 --> 00:10:46,305
Sesat lagi?

90
00:10:54,423 --> 00:10:55,426
Maaf.

91
00:10:57,971 --> 00:10:59,884
Macam mana nak balik ke universiti?

92
00:11:00,226 --> 00:11:01,921
Saya tak pergi arah tu.

93
00:11:02,216 --> 00:11:03,346
Itu arah lain.

94
00:11:03,995 --> 00:11:05,700
Jadi awak nak pergi mana?

95
00:11:05,884 --> 00:11:08,234
Saya nak ke Tha Phae Walking Street.
Ada orang suruh saya ambil dia.

96
00:11:10,800 --> 00:11:11,823
Walking street?

97
00:11:14,087 --> 00:11:14,783
Ya.

98
00:11:15,016 --> 00:11:16,506
Kalau macam tu, naiklah.

99
00:12:17,192 --> 00:12:17,754
Alamak.

100
00:12:19,291 --> 00:12:20,207
Maaf.

101
00:12:26,601 --> 00:12:27,749
Phoon.

102
00:12:30,222 --> 00:12:31,564
Kau ingat aku, Fah?

103
00:12:38,349 --> 00:12:38,970
Ya.

104
00:12:41,417 --> 00:12:44,241
Lama betul. Hampir empat tahun, kan?

105
00:12:44,736 --> 00:12:46,795
Apa khabar, Phoon? Kau okey?

106
00:12:49,745 --> 00:12:50,848
Aku okey.

107
00:12:51,626 --> 00:12:52,351
Betul?

108
00:12:52,576 --> 00:12:53,998
Kau buat apa kat sini seorang diri?

109
00:12:58,368 --> 00:13:00,881
Oh—Tonfah. Lama tak jumpa.

110
00:13:01,222 --> 00:13:03,429
Aku sihat. Kau pula?

111
00:13:03,597 --> 00:13:06,389
Kami pun okey. Kau datang seorang?

112
00:13:06,758 --> 00:13:08,894
Ya, tapi aku nak balik sekejap lagi.

113
00:13:14,472 --> 00:13:16,920
Phoon. Phoon.

114
00:13:18,152 --> 00:13:19,798
Phoon. Phoon.

115
00:13:20,955 --> 00:13:21,933
Phoon.

116
00:13:27,598 --> 00:13:28,757
P'Fah.

117
00:13:39,792 --> 00:13:43,546
Aku nampak si kecil ni berlari tepi jalan masa hujan,

118
00:13:44,275 --> 00:13:46,887
jadi kau ikut dia sampai sesat kat sini, kan?

119
00:13:52,475 --> 00:13:53,210
Ya.

120
00:13:54,208 --> 00:13:57,195
Maaf sebab susahkan P'Fah lagi.

121
00:13:58,346 --> 00:13:59,576
Tak ada masalah.

122
00:14:03,477 --> 00:14:05,010
Apa aku dah cakap?

123
00:14:05,459 --> 00:14:08,117
Kalau sesat, duduk saja dan tunggu.

124
00:14:08,339 --> 00:14:10,211
Aku akan datang cari kau sendiri.

125
00:14:23,102 --> 00:14:24,425
Aku dah jumpa kau.

126
00:14:45,877 --> 00:14:47,407
Jadi kau memang belajar kat sini?

127
00:14:47,885 --> 00:14:49,485
Aku ingat kau datang bercuti saja.

128
00:14:49,709 --> 00:14:52,339
Semester pun belum mula lagi, dua bulan lagi.

129
00:14:54,964 --> 00:14:57,035
Aku cuma nak cuba tinggal sini dulu.

130
00:14:58,281 --> 00:15:00,240
Banyak lagi aku kena sesuaikan diri.

131
00:15:01,404 --> 00:15:04,662
Kenapa kau pilih belajar jauh seorang diri?

132
00:15:05,785 --> 00:15:06,795
Err...

133
00:15:07,288 --> 00:15:08,968
Aku cuma nak cuba.

134
00:15:11,967 --> 00:15:13,211
Kau fakulti apa?

135
00:15:14,244 --> 00:15:15,521
Perubatan Veterinar.

136
00:15:18,586 --> 00:15:20,891
Aku ingat kau tak suka bidang tu.

137
00:15:22,157 --> 00:15:25,164
Tak, sebenarnya aku agak suka.

138
00:15:27,678 --> 00:15:28,531
Dan...

139
00:15:28,619 --> 00:15:30,450
Kau belajar perubatan, kan?

140
00:15:31,165 --> 00:15:31,922
Ya.

141
00:15:37,794 --> 00:15:38,682
Terima kasih.

142
00:15:43,300 --> 00:15:46,354
Aku ingat aku takkan jumpa kau lagi, Phoon.

143
00:15:49,518 --> 00:15:50,628
Ya...

144
00:15:53,696 --> 00:15:54,408
Oh—

145
00:15:54,718 --> 00:15:56,044
Jadi kau datang sini seorang?

146
00:15:56,139 --> 00:15:57,370
Kau datang dengan kawan-kawan tak?

147
00:15:59,345 --> 00:16:00,122
Aku datang seorang.

148
00:16:00,657 --> 00:16:01,445
Betul?

149
00:16:01,911 --> 00:16:02,776
Hebatnya.

150
00:16:10,727 --> 00:16:12,280
Kau tak banyak berubah pun, Phoon.

151
00:16:13,272 --> 00:16:14,748
Kau nampak sama saja.

152
00:16:16,417 --> 00:16:17,945
Terus teringat masa kita kecil dulu.

153
00:16:18,162 --> 00:16:19,182
Masa tu,

154
00:16:19,948 --> 00:16:21,357
kita asyik bersama.

155
00:16:22,114 --> 00:16:23,509
Kau, aku, dan Fun juga.

156
00:16:29,589 --> 00:16:32,389
Oh ya, ayah kau macam mana?

157
00:16:32,811 --> 00:16:36,158
Dah lama tak dengar sejak kau pindah.

158
00:16:39,588 --> 00:16:41,322
Dia okey saja.

159
00:16:42,124 --> 00:16:44,408
- Mm.
- Mak aku...

160
00:16:46,617 --> 00:16:48,853
Aku pun tak pasti dia macam mana.

161
00:16:52,757 --> 00:16:53,874
Maksud kau?

162
00:16:58,266 --> 00:16:59,814
Mak ayah aku bercerai.

163
00:17:00,598 --> 00:17:02,106
Lepas tu mak aku pindah keluar.

164
00:17:05,131 --> 00:17:06,619
Maaf, Phoon.

165
00:17:06,980 --> 00:17:08,081
Kau okey?

166
00:17:13,160 --> 00:17:14,438
Fun macam mana?

167
00:17:24,537 --> 00:17:26,151
Fun okey saja.

168
00:18:09,105 --> 00:18:10,767
Terima kasih hantar aku balik.

169
00:18:11,189 --> 00:18:12,805
Pandu elok-elok.

170
00:18:13,059 --> 00:18:14,592
Okey. Jumpa lagi.

171
00:18:15,028 --> 00:18:15,622
Ya.

172
00:19:14,912 --> 00:19:15,727
Kepada: Torfun

173
00:19:45,281 --> 00:19:47,142
Torfun yang aku sayang,

174
00:19:48,271 --> 00:19:50,481
Hari ni aku terserempak P'Fah.

175
00:19:50,939 --> 00:19:52,152
Aku betul-betul terkejut.

176
00:19:52,697 --> 00:19:54,106
Aku tak tahu nak buat apa.

177
00:19:55,130 --> 00:19:57,216
Banyak benda aku nak cakap pada dia,

178
00:19:57,386 --> 00:20:00,554
tapi bila tiba masanya, aku kelu.

179
00:20:00,988 --> 00:20:03,462
Dia nampak gembira jumpa aku.

180
00:20:04,309 --> 00:20:05,945
Dia siap tanya pasal kau.

181
00:20:06,253 --> 00:20:07,924
Dan akhirnya aku menipu,

182
00:20:08,237 --> 00:20:10,875
cakap kau okey saja.

183
00:20:32,160 --> 00:20:34,693
Maaf sebab aku menipu dia macam tu.

184
00:20:35,391 --> 00:20:38,051
Aku takut kalau dia tahu hal sebenar,

185
00:20:38,614 --> 00:20:40,848
dia akan kecewa dengan aku.

186
00:20:41,934 --> 00:20:46,314
Dia mungkin marah, macam mak ayah aku.

187
00:20:47,242 --> 00:20:49,229
Kau dah tak ada,

188
00:20:49,871 --> 00:20:52,271
dan kalau P'Fah pun tak ada dengan aku,

189
00:20:52,928 --> 00:20:54,586
siapa lagi yang tinggal untuk aku?

190
00:21:27,162 --> 00:21:28,512
Kau menipu aku, kan?

191
00:21:30,282 --> 00:21:32,408
- Tak, aku tak menipu.
- Aku dah tahu pasal Fun.

192
00:21:33,294 --> 00:21:36,922
Teruk betul... apa kau buat, dan menipu aku.

193
00:21:39,029 --> 00:21:40,349
Ada lagi benda kau tipu aku?

194
00:21:41,567 --> 00:21:42,431
Hah?

195
00:21:46,354 --> 00:21:48,373
Aku betul-betul kecewa dengan kau, Phoon.

196
00:21:49,250 --> 00:21:52,524
Kau sakiti semua orang, terutama Fun.

197
00:21:52,666 --> 00:21:55,441
Kalau dulu kau tak buat begitu, Fun takkan mati.

198
00:21:55,552 --> 00:21:57,413
Kau sedar tak, kau yang bersalah?

199
00:21:58,447 --> 00:21:59,136
Ya.

200
00:22:02,435 --> 00:22:03,565
Satu lagi...

201
00:22:04,266 --> 00:22:05,951
Aku benci penipu.

202
00:22:06,807 --> 00:22:09,496
Dan aku tak boleh maafkan orang yang asyik sakiti orang.

203
00:22:10,871 --> 00:22:12,454
Lebih baik kita tak jumpa lagi.

204
00:22:14,484 --> 00:22:16,527
P'Fah, aku minta maaf.

205
00:22:16,552 --> 00:22:18,528
- Lepaskan.
- P'Fah.

206
00:22:18,641 --> 00:22:20,823
P'Fah, aku minta maaf.

207
00:22:20,903 --> 00:22:22,721
P'Fah.

208
00:22:23,314 --> 00:22:25,419
P'Fah, aku minta maaf.

209
00:22:25,949 --> 00:22:31,120
P'Fah, tolong jangan tinggalkan aku.

210
00:22:32,940 --> 00:22:34,653
Tolong jangan tinggalkan aku, P'Fah.

211
00:22:48,891 --> 00:22:49,946
Terima kasih.

212
00:23:01,625 --> 00:23:03,226
Dua cucuk khinzir dan satu pulut, ya.

213
00:23:03,475 --> 00:23:05,611
Baik, sayang. Kenapa makan sikit sangat?

214
00:23:08,745 --> 00:23:09,728
Kau tak sihat ke?

215
00:23:10,192 --> 00:23:11,727
Kau nampak pucat sikit.

216
00:23:13,410 --> 00:23:14,334
Tak.

217
00:23:15,875 --> 00:23:16,493
Nah.

218
00:23:16,577 --> 00:23:18,373
- Berapa?
- 20 baht.

219
00:23:21,622 --> 00:23:22,564
Terima kasih.

220
00:26:16,817 --> 00:26:18,640
Bateri aku nak habis.

221
00:26:40,845 --> 00:26:42,690
- Mari sini. Sekarang.
- Aduh!

222
00:26:42,842 --> 00:26:44,257
Aku dah cakap mari sini!

223
00:26:44,714 --> 00:26:46,539
Masuk. Pergi dalam.

224
00:26:46,703 --> 00:26:48,623
Kau tahu tak apa yang kau dah buat?

225
00:26:49,300 --> 00:26:53,011
Berapa kali aku cakap jangan masuk pejabat aku?

226
00:26:53,125 --> 00:26:57,588
Kau tahu pasu tu lagi mahal daripada nyawa kau?

227
00:26:57,797 --> 00:26:59,142
Ingat betul-betul.

228
00:26:59,336 --> 00:27:01,602
Duduk sini. Jangan pergi mana-mana.

229
00:27:02,794 --> 00:27:04,336
Ayah... Ayah...

230
00:27:04,377 --> 00:27:06,413
- Berhenti menangis.
- Ayah, maafkan saya.

231
00:27:06,540 --> 00:27:10,509
Ayah, maaf. Saya takkan buat lagi.

232
00:27:10,605 --> 00:27:12,354
- Jangan panggil aku.
- Ayah...

233
00:27:12,400 --> 00:27:14,312
Budak tak guna. Diam.

234
00:27:15,314 --> 00:27:18,816
P'Fah! Fun! Tolong... tolong aku!

235
00:27:19,388 --> 00:27:22,142
- Phoon, kau di dalam ke?
- P'Fah, tolong aku.

236
00:27:23,060 --> 00:27:25,451
Gelap sangat. Aku takut, P'Fah.

237
00:27:25,450 --> 00:27:27,237
Tenang, Phoon.

238
00:27:27,259 --> 00:27:29,441
Memang gelap dalam tu.

239
00:27:30,242 --> 00:27:31,654
Hulurkan tangan kau.

240
00:27:33,131 --> 00:27:36,740
Jangan takut. Aku teman sampai Uncle Kong balik.

241
00:27:37,271 --> 00:27:39,459
Jangan pergi mana-mana, P'Fah.

242
00:27:58,877 --> 00:28:01,257
Helo, P'Fah. Sekarang boleh cakap?

243
00:28:01,925 --> 00:28:03,167
Ada apa-apa tak kena?

244
00:28:04,874 --> 00:28:07,282
Err... cuma di asrama aku--

245
00:28:07,791 --> 00:28:08,887
bekalan elektrik terputus.

246
