Jadi kami putus.

506
00:51:08,265 --> 00:51:09,768
Lepas tu,

507
00:51:10,174 --> 00:51:12,635
aku dah tak cari cinta lagi.

508
00:51:15,805 --> 00:51:17,305
Faham.

509
00:51:22,512 --> 00:51:23,900
Dia siap cakap

510
00:51:25,549 --> 00:51:28,051
aku macam langit dia.

511
00:51:30,330 --> 00:51:31,921
Aku tak pernah nak jadi macam tu.

512
00:51:37,121 --> 00:51:38,142
Bila hujan,

513
00:51:38,917 --> 00:51:40,600
langit tak cantik.

514
00:51:41,225 --> 00:51:42,696
Tak ada orang nak tengok.

515
00:51:45,417 --> 00:51:48,041
Tapi orang harap langit cantik setiap hari.

516
00:51:52,450 --> 00:51:53,484
Aku

517
00:51:54,263 --> 00:51:55,921
tak boleh jadi langit sesiapa.

518
00:52:01,219 --> 00:52:03,005
Tak bolehkah kau jadi

519
00:52:03,951 --> 00:52:05,321
langit aku?

520
00:52:27,653 --> 00:52:29,968
Kawan? Siapa nama dia?

521
00:52:31,374 --> 00:52:32,568
Johan.

522
00:52:33,019 --> 00:52:34,954
- Minat?
- Tak.

523
00:52:35,365 --> 00:52:36,580
Aku nak ambil peperiksaan perubatan.

524
00:52:36,607 --> 00:52:40,915
Boleh kau tutor aku, Fah?

525
00:52:41,334 --> 00:52:46,854
Di Mawsynram, India, hujan lebih 10,800 mm setahun—
lebih kurang sembilan kali ganda dari sini.

526
00:52:47,165 --> 00:52:48,478
Langit nampak cantik hari ni.

527
00:52:48,668 --> 00:52:51,717
Bagus bila langit boleh buat kau senyum begini.

528
00:52:52,708 --> 00:52:53,595
Phoon,

529
00:52:54,065 --> 00:52:55,391
teruskan senyum, okey?

